name: Genshin Impact Landscapes
description:
My first LoRA that I am confident enough in to release to the public. Trained it on 768x768 screenshots from Genshin Impact. Can generate region-specific landscapes (Mondstadt, Liyue, Inazuma, Dragonspine, Sumeru desert, Sumeru jungle). Can be used in conjunction with a character LoRA to give an authentic backdrop. For example, what would it look like if Yoimiya visited the Sumeru desert.

Tested with Anything-v4.5 and various mixes based on it. CLIP skip = 2 recommended.

modelVersions.description:
• Added more images to the training set

  • Improved tags

  • Removed a few lower quality images

Just like the previous version, this one can be used in conjunction with character LoRAs to add an authentic backdrop. Be aware that the character LoRA might have its own idea on what the backdrop should look like (especially if it's overfitted or had a small training set), or it might not work at all (I couldn't get Nahida's LoRA to work with my LoRA for example).
